1. "if ns.runtaintManager {"
2. "if nc.taintManager != nil {
 Can you please unify it?

Or even better, You can move all those checks to TaintManager implementation. E.g.
```
func (tm *taintManager) NodeUpdated(...) {
  if tm == nil {
    return
  }
  // Now real body
}
```

With this pattern you can omit all those "ifs" here and this code will be much cleaner and shorter.

